{
  "stem": "24409.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He said, you will never get them back from me [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But at [INAUDIBLE] we'll get them back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We take, I think his said, as account payment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't know whether I suggested it or that it was his idea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyhow, he accepted a down payment of 2,000 pounds, and immediately a ship was sent which was then in a port in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Was sent to Fiume.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That was the most [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Draga was supposed to arrive the next morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And in the evening I heard that Eichmann had decided not to radio.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We promised him all the time, tomorrow, in two days, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There had been about two weeks in this [INAUDIBLE], which was very bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because for the sudden diarrhea, they had to use the toilets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And this collected on the bottom of the wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Or then they were permitted to go out but under another guard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the guards took Jews to relieve themselves outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But there was no food or nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when he ordered them back, I called and talked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eichmann said, when the ships [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, if the ship is not there by 5:00 in the afternoon-- that was when it came the next morning-- they all go back to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I told him, I think the ship will be here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you go to Dachau, you know that here these are disciplined people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are under orders to be ready to fulfilll to repeat what people did at the-- what is the rock?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Masada.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will commit suicide, and you will have an international scandal on our hands, which at this point, Germany doesn't want, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That you do not want, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very furious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He hung up.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
